data.description: IN SEARCH OF A SIMPLER LIFE?! LET THIS HOME BE THE BEGINNING. MOVE-IN READY AND CONVENIENT LOCATION MAKE THIS HOME A WINNER. LIVE SPACIOUSLY ON THE MAIN LEVEL WITH A WELL-THOUGHT-OUT FLOOR PLAN. A GENEROUS LIVING ROOM FLOWS EFFORTLESSLY INTO AN EAT-IN KITCHEN WITH AMPLE GRANITE COUNTER SPACE, CABINETRY, WALK-IN PANTRY AND LARGE ISLAND. RELAXATION AND ENTERTAINING ARE A BREEZE WITH ACCESS OFF THE MAIN LEVEL TO THE COVERED PATIO AND FENCED-IN BACKYARD. RETREAT UPSTAIRS TO THE PRIMARY SUITE AND TWO ADDITIONAL BEDROOMS. THE LARGE PRIMARY SUITE FEATURES DOUBLE SINKS AND A WALK-IN CLOSET. A GUEST BATHROOM AND THE LAUNDRY ROOM ARE CONVENIENTLY LOCATED OFF THE UPSTAIRS HALLWAY. COME SEE THIS WINNING HOME TODAY!
